Summary: Red individual lights in a circle.
divs: Sighting DetailsIt was traveling from NE to SW, , at one point I thought it was a became brighter. At one point I thought it was a asteroid or comet rushing towards the planet. It hovered for about 30 seconds from a great distance away. Then it traveled NW at a high rate of speed and was not seen again as it disappeared into space. It was far away. Seriously looked like a asteroid or something until it took off towards the NW and outerspace.
